  <h1>Business Applications Reference</h1>
  
  <a href="businessApplicationsMapTileById.page" title="Map Tile by Id">
    
  <b>Map Tile by Id</b>
  </a>
  <p>
    The <a href="businessApplicationsMapTileById.page">Map Tile by Id</a> business application will return the metadata for the map tile with the specified map tile id.
    This Business Application is used to obtain the Map Tile Boundary of a specific map, a polygon made up of the requested number of latitude/longitude points.
  </p>
  <a href="businessApplicationsMapTileByLocation.page">
  <b>Map Tile by Location</b>
  </a>
  <p>
    The <a href="businessApplicationsMapTileByLocation.page">Map Tile by Id Business Application</a> will return the metadata for the map tile of a given map grid and scale identified as containing the specified latitude/longitude location.
    An example of a use of this Business Application would be to find out the NTS 1:50000 map name containing a specific geographic location, such as a town or mountain peak, for which you knew the latitude and longitude.
  </p>
</div>
